Oh, man. We have another new enemy here: Red Bubbles. They're just like the regular flashing Bubbles, in that they're invincible and don't damage your life meter. However, if they hit you, you lose the ability to swing your sword permanently!

...Blue Bubbles! Bump into one of them and you'll be able to swing your sword again. And, since they never harm you, and only return your sword-swinging ability if you've lost it, I would consider these guys friends, not enemies.
